<plot>Comedy in 3 parts. The first one, called "O Padre e a Modelo", tells the story of a young man who, in order to conquer his shyness, seeks help with an actors' teacher, who forces him to dress like a priest. In these clothes, he meets a very sexy actress. In the second story, a middle-aged man tries to confront his sexual problems in a motel. In the third, a man suffering from claustrophobia has to hide inside a closet, when his lover's aunt arrives unexpectedly.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?046974</url></doc>
